1107977885095063552.text:
9. Theoretical reward rate = inflation rate / staking ratio
= 7% / 32.40% = 21.60%
10. Actual reward rate = actual inflation rate /staking ratio
= 5.18% / 32.40% = 15.98%(5.61% less than 21.60%)

1107977883606089729.text:
6. actual block per year = seconds in 1y / actual blocktime
= 365.25 * 24 * 60 * 60 / 6.75 = 4,675,200 blocks
7. actual total inflation atom in 1y = 2.62 atom * 4,675,200 = 12,249,024 atom
8. actual yearly inflation rate = 12,249,024 / 236,382,221 = 5.18%(1.82p% less than 7%)

1107977882222026754.text:
Derivation of "actual" inflation

1. Total atom supply = 236,382,221 atom
2. inflation = 7%
3. inflation atom per year = 236,382,221 * 7% = 16,546,755 atom
4. block per year = 6,311,520(defined in genesis)
5. inflation atom per block = 16,546,755 atom / 6,311,520 = 2.62 atom
